rComments: Awesome prof. Very helpful and is very easy to approach with questions or concerns. Exams are exactly as he says they are and there are no surprises. I thought the content itself was a little dry but he made the best of it. Would definitely take another one of his classes.

Amazing! I believe this was his first time teaching a full course, though if he wouldn't have mentioned it, definitely wouldn't have been able to tell. Super helpful in clarifying topics, funny & genuinely concerned for students' success. Lectures were interesting, assignments offered considerable freedom & expectations on exams were very clear.
